  "remarks": "\nLuis Miguel Martínez Morales (“Martínez”) is an involved person within the meaning of the Global Anti-Corruption Sanctions Regulations 2021 on the basis of the following ground: Martínez is associated with a person who is or has been involved in serious corruption, namely Alejandro Eduardo Giammattei Falla.\n",
